title: Windows Activation Seven Loader 1.9.4 November 2010 WAT
description:
Here is the famous Windows Loader module activation of DAZ (formerly "Windows 7 Loader") based
on the old Windows 7 Orbit30 Loader. Easy to access, a clean install & effectively
differs from other loaders often outdated or too complicated, containing malware
or simply not working. Windows Loader is becoming one of the few to offer loaders
activation of all versions of Windows 7, Windows Vista and Windows Server 2008
all languages and compatible with the x86 (32 Bit) & x64 (64 bits)!
Windows 7 Loader changed its name to Windows Loader to highlight its compatibility
with all new generation systems from Microsoft. Thank you to DAZ for his outstanding work!

*** This release does not contain malware detection if it is a false positive ***
*** Remember to start the program administrator (right click + "Run as Administrator") ***

Once Windows loader open, make sure the light is green light, then click "Install" to make your Windows Server 2008/R2 7/Vista or original.
